{"tid":1323890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1999年勇武派 feat. 候志強","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T12:19:23.000Z","uid":235546,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea0878d508635cea4afd70d6f816184a2a9b1c5","tid":1323890,"uid":235546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:44:27.000Z","msg":"1999年11月上水石湖新村警民衝突!<br />\n新界人勇武抗爭方式! 掟石，水喉鐵，開山刀，引爆石油器，淋電油，汽油彈，到處放火等。<br />\n<br />\n1999年11月16日新界上水<br />\n為紓緩新界北區水患，香港政府進行梧桐河防洪及擴闊工程，上水石湖新村有33個包括廠家及商戶不滿賠償及安排，拒絕遷出，警民引爆激烈衝突!<br />\n<br />\n#歴史時空<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/648757011816916/posts/3410247539001169?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F648757011816916%2Fposts%2F3410247539001169%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=a4461852\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/648757011816916/posts/3410247539001169?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc309881e9fc3cafe2934098a376556b31a84bce","tid":1323890,"uid":235546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:47:50.000Z","msg":"一齊探討吓歷史"},{"pid":"37d0b7752f6aafd037a4cc5e912757b34cd8c35c","tid":1323890,"uid":235546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce4b0ddad1e66ccd220a667a98d6b3334cdf345","tid":1323890,"uid":235546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"嗰時有埋消防vs示威者"},{"pid":"e797ee7b8f7c59c68900b32cec669c882996f264","tid":1323890,"uid":235546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:55:11.000Z","msg":"以前就真係叫克制"},{"pid":"6431c1648ed621277918c74e18bcc0f0fa78bfd5","tid":1323890,"uid":260181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:58:28.000Z","msg":"好撚勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class